OnNeedlePoke
{
	//i wont increment silence here if you interrupt her by poking because teeecchnically you arent being silent youre nag nagging her
	
	"\s[0]...?"
	
	if silence >= anger1
	{
		"\s[0]\i[302]Oh, now you want to bother me?\w8\w8 ...\w8\s[2]You mortals are so funny."
		"\s[0]\i[402]Oh, I thought you were busy ignoring me.\w8\w8 \i[200]You mortals and your whims."
	}
	else
	{
		"\s[2]...Hello!\w8\w8 \i[403]Oh, you're just so CUTE!"
		"\s[0]--Oh, huh?\w8\w8 ...\w8\s[2]\i[403]Ehehe, where did you get that?\w8\w8 That's a funny looking needle."
		"\s[0]--Hm?\w8\w8 ...\w8\s[0]\i[403]What are you doing with that, mortal?\w8\w8 \i[301]You could get hurt!"
		"\s[0]--Hm?\w8\w8 ...\w8\s[2]\i[403]Ehe. \w8\w8What a small needle..."
		"\s[0]--Huh?\w8\w8 ...\w8\s[2]\i[403]Awwww, it's so small!"
		"\s[0]--Hm.\w8\w8 \s[0]\i[403]You know, mortal, that almost reminds me of my old needle...\w8\w8 \s[2]\i[202]Of course, it's much bigger than this one.\w8\w8 \s[0]\i[403]And currently stuck in the sky of the Bramblebrush.\w8\w8 \s[2]\i[202]\i[403]I do miss that old thing..."
		"\s[0]\i[200]\i[403]Ooh, I should pick up sewing again, shouldn't I?\w8\w8 \s[2]\i[404]I taught all my siblings how to sew, you know.\w8\w8 \s[0]\i[200]\i[302]\i[404]Not like Fenr picked any of it up, though."
	}
}

